        "title": "Primefaces ManyCheckbox to array",
        "body": "<p>I got the following problem.\nI got a datatable in a datatable\nExample:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;p:dataTable var=\"mainarea\"&gt;\n  ...\n  &lt;p:dataTable value=\"#{bean.subarea(mainarea)\" selection=\"#{bean.selectedsubarea}\"&gt;\n    &lt;p:colum selectionMode=\"multiple\"/&gt;\n     ...\n  &lt;/p:dataTable&gt;\n&lt;/p:dataTable&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>It works fine as long as the first table only generates 1 result.<\/p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/TeQSU.gif\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n\n<p>But as soon as there are 2 tables ill get a NullPointerException.<\/p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/ymPdY.gif\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n\n<p>The problem should be that I need to write into #{bean.selectedsubarea[x]} so every subarea list got his own array but I dont know how to realise that.<\/p>\n\n<p>Thanks for your help :-)<\/p>\n",
